strings:
<voice_0x01000B4F><se_def>*: Not now!
I've almost got this game in the bag!
<voice_0x01000B50><se_low>*: What!?

<voice_0x01000B51><se_low>*: You little runt!
You must be cheating!

<voice_0x01000B52><se_low>Yangus: Take it easy!
No need to get excited!
I know it 'urts when ya lose an' all, but...

<voice_0x01000B53><se_low>*: What!?
...Oh, I get it!
<voice_0x01000B54><se_low>*: You're with him!

<voice_0x01000B55><se_low>Yangus: Oi! You wanna watch it!
Don't go throwin' accusions about!
You don't wanna get on my wrong side!

<voice_0x01000B56><se_high>Jessica: Take it easy, you guys!
What are you, a couple of cavemen?
<voice_0x01000B57><se_def>*: What are you doing!?

<voice_0x01000B58><se_def>*: Think you'll get away with that just cos you're
a lady?

<voice_0x01000B59><se_low>Yangus: Wot's wiv you two, eh!?
Two blokes gangin' up on one bird!
Behave!

<voice_0x01000B5A><se_low>*: That's it, you oaf!
Those are my mates!

<voice_0x01000B5B><se_def>*: So who are you?
You don't look like Simpletons to me...

<voice_0x01000B5C><se_def>*: Anyway, I owe you one.
Thanks to you, I managed to pull that little caper off without being caught.

<voice_0x01000B5D><se_def>*: He was such an easy mark,
I got a bit carried away.

<voice_0x01000B5E><se_def>*: Still, can't hang around.
Don't want any more trouble!
<voice_0x01000B5F><se_high>Jessica: ...What!?

<voice_0x01000B60><se_def>*: I hope you weren't hurt by my little jape?
Are you all right?

<voice_0x01000B61><se_high>Jessica: You're out of luck! I'm fine!
Apart from you leering at me!

<voice_0x01000B62><se_def>*: By way of thanks for helping me,
and as a memento of our...‘encounter’...

<voice_0x01000B63><se_def>*: The name's Angelo.
I live at Maella Abbey.

<voice_0x01000B64><se_def>Angelo: Show them that ring if you'd like to see me.
I'll be expecting you!

<voice_0x01000B65><se_def>Angelo: Au revoir, for now!
Maella Abbey, all right?
Just ask for Angelo!
Don't forget!

<voice_0x01000B66><se_low>Yangus: Oh, 'ere you are, guv!
I been lookin' all over for ya.

<voice_0x01000B67><se_low>Yangus: Gave that lot wot for!
He he he!

<voice_0x01000B68><se_high>Jessica: Hey, <hero>!
I hope you don't plan on keeping this ring!

<voice_0x01000B69><se_high>Jessica: We're going to Maella Abbey right now
to give it back to that smarmy cheat.
Whether he likes it or not!
